$ Excel Object Model: CommandBars("Ply")

{ Disable the right click on a sheet tab #xls-disable-right-click-on-sheet-tab

  Using the `CommandBar` named *Ply*, it is possible to disable right clicks on a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Sheet-tabs[sheet tabs]
  gh|about-MS-Office-object-model|/Excel/CommandBars/Ply.vb||

  Thus, after running `disable_right_click_on_sheet_tab`, the following right click is not possible anymore:
  gh|about-MS-Office-object-model|/Excel/CommandBars/img/Ply.png||

}

sa:
  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/CommandBars[Excel's `CommandBars` object]
